Files Updated in Existing Services
File	Change
booking-service/SecurityConfig.java	Added permitAll for GET /bookings/internal/** and PATCH /bookings/internal/cancel/**
booking-service/BookingService.java	Added getBookingByIdInternal() + cancelBookingInternal()
booking-service/BookingController.java	Added GET /bookings/internal/{id} + PATCH /bookings/internal/cancel/{id}
api-gateway/application.yml	Added cancellation-service route + circuit breaker
pom.xml (parent)	Added <module>cancellation-service</module>
Refund Policy (time before departure)
Hours Before Departure	Refund %
> 48 hours	90%
24 – 48 hours	75%
12 – 24 hours	50%
6 – 12 hours	25%
< 6 hours	0% (No refund, but still cancelled)
Already departed	REJECTED (cannot cancel)
PENDING_PAYMENT	Free cancel (no payment was collected)
API Endpoints (port 8086 / via gateway localhost:8080)
POST  /cancellations/initiate           → UC6 Steps 1-5 (full workflow)
GET   /cancellations/my                 → User's cancellation history
GET   /cancellations/{id}               → By ID
GET   /cancellations/reference/{ref}    → By CAN-XXXXXXXX
GET   /cancellations/booking/{bookingId}→ By booking ID
GET   /cancellations          (ADMIN)   → All records
GET   /cancellations/health             → Health check

